  <title>GLib.HOOK_FLAG_USER_SHIFT</title>
  <p>The position of the first bit which is not reserved for internal
use be the <link xref="GLib.Hook"/> implementation, i.e.
`1 &lt;&lt; G_HOOK_FLAG_USER_SHIFT` is the first
bit which can be used for application-defined flags.</p>

